room_title: Escape room "The Doll Room" by Gulf Coast Escape Room in Destin
room_description: There was a little girl who was very demented to her dolls. One day the dolls had enough and she is no longer with us but her spirit was left behind. It is your job to find her spirit and release and get out of the room within 60 min. before the dolls decide to trap you in the room forever.
